krataiwqhnai dia tou pneumatov autou eiv ton esw anqrwpon
     3:17 katoikhsai ton criston dia thv pistewv en taiv
kardiaiv umwn
     3:18 en agaph errizwmenoi kai teqemeliwmenoi ina
exiscushte katalabesqai sun pasin toiv agioiv ti to platov
kai mhkov kai baqov kai uyov
     3:19 gnwnai te thn uperballousan thv gnwsewv agaphn tou
